  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Albuns
    This class represents the Album page
    Artists
    This class represents the Artists page
    CreatePlaylist
    This class represents the Create Playlist page
    Flags
    This class just holds some boolean to control the MusicThread so it behaves properly
    LastPlayed
    This class show us the last played songs by a specific user
    Logged
    This class represents the homePage of the user
    Main
    This Class controls the GUI page changes and reset the tables so there is never duplicated results on tables Most of its methods are self explanatory
    MusicThread
    This class represents the Thread that is created to play the music when such is required It uses an external library (TinySound) that simplifies a lot of the process
    MyPlaylists
    This class represents the playlists from a certain user and allows us to access a specific playlist
    MySongs
    This class represents the songs that belong to a user allowing us to play them
    NotLogged
    This class represents the first page presented to the user where login can be made
